AUDIO: 'I wanted to make Twitter suck less. So, I deleted the entire app. But, wait. I actually want my feed. I want to see fun memes and news about local politics and events that connect me with people. That\'s why I made'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Bouncer, a way to filter out the slop and heal [music] your feed. Just describe what you want to get rid of and watch the tweets disappear. Find a tweet annoying, but don\'t know why? Just click this button and we\'ll suggest some new phrases to filter this tweet and others'

[00:24] [scene:talk]
